      "id": "581530f7_be83b760",
      "file_path": "docs/sections/tls_enablement.rst",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 21,
      "message": "I've marked this entire section as obsolete.  It doesn't make sense to try to make it generic, since it's specifically about Cloudify deployments.\n\nI would have removed this section entirely (it should have been removed several releases ago), but the section below about Helm deployment looks incomplete to me.  (For instance, it doesn't say anything about the contents of the certificate directory.)   Unfortunately, I don't know enough about how the external certificate process works to be able to create good documentation for the Helm deployment.   We need the external TLS developers to make these changes.\n\nThe alternative is to remove this section completely and just hope that the section on Helm deployment is sufficient.",
